prodNameC: 常盈甲型胎兒蛋白酵素免疫連結分析法
ingredientsDesc:
Anti-AFP-Coated Microtitration Strips：
One stripholder containing 96 microtitration wells coated with anti-AFP antibody.
AFP Standard A / Sample Diluent：
One bottle, 5.0 mL, labeled A, containing 0 ng/mL AFP in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
AFP Standard B-F：
Five vials, 0.6 mL each, labeled B-F, containing concentrations of approximately 5, 20, 100, 200 and 500 ng/mL AFP in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
AFP Controls：
Two vials, 0.6 mL each, Levels I and II, containing low and high concentrations of AFP in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
Assay Buffer ： (GREEN)
One bottle, 2.8 mL, containing a protein-based buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
AFP Antibody-Enzyme Conjugate Concentrate：
One vial, 0.5 mL,  containing anti-AFP antibody conjugated to the enzyme horseradish peroxidase in a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a non-mercury preservative. Dilute prior to use in Assay Buffer A.
TMB Chromogen Solution
